r eyes the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" inflicted great and devastating signs and wonders on Egypt, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 9:10","book":"Neh","chapter":9,"verse":10,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 135:9","book":"Psa","chapter":135,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 20:3","book":"Isa","chapter":20,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jr 32:20","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":20,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" on Pharaoh, and on all his household, "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Neh 9:10","book":"Neh","chapter":9,"verse":10},{"label":"Ps 135:9","book":"Psa","chapter":135,"verse":9},{"label":"Is 20:3","book":"Isa","chapter":20,"verse":3},{"label":"Jr 32:20","book":"Jer","chapter":32,"verse":20}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:6:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"but he brought us from there in order to lead us in and give us the land that he swore to our ancestors. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:6:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"The "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" commanded us to follow all these statutes and to fear the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" our God for our prosperity always and for our preservation, as it is today. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Deu:6:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Righteousness will be ours if we are careful to follow every one of these commands before the "},{"kind":"text","text":"Lord","style":"divine"},{"kind":"text","text":" our God, as he has commanded us.’"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783280289954}